n\nSo for `2.2`:\n- success path: returns the class\n- failure path: throws `ClassNotFoundException`\n- fallback path at line `75`: effectively unreachable\n\nWhat I already fixed:\n- Updated the test to match real `2.2` behavior by asserting `ClassNotFoundException` instead of expecting fallback.\n\nCurrent test commit:\n- `e5a562525` — `Adjust commons-io 2.2 class resolution test`\n\nConclusion:\n- I do not recommend adding another test here, because it would not be able to cover that remaining call site without relying on impossible/non-JVM behavior.\n- The dynamic-access report for this specific call site appears to be a false reachable target for `2.2`.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0838a8bb5a62b6810169eff190375c81909acabc3b5372ca67\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.4", "usage": {"input": 1334, "output": 789, "cacheRead": 27008, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29131, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777332614277, "responseId": "resp_0838a8bb5a62b6810169eff18710a4819081d0f7c4577fe9a2"}}
